name: 张祥森
bio_zh: 我目前是西北工业大学自动化学院的七年级（2019年-至今）博士研究生，师从韩军伟教授。我的研究兴趣包括多视图分类、医学图像和多模态处理。
bio_en: I am currently a seventh-year (2019 - present) doctoral student at the School of Automation, Northwestern Polytechnical University, under the supervision of Professor Han Junwei. My research interests include multi-view classification, medical image processing, and multi-modal processing.
research_interests: 医学图像分析、多模态处理
